      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some minor dings, and while the interior is functional, there is visible wear on the upholstery and carpet. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, but it may require some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape. It's a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind a bit of character and cosmetic imperfection.",
