    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this beauty! It\u2019s in absolutely incredible condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale, so come grab a total steal before someone else does! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
